{"id":232746258,"title":"2020最期待BL泰劇-千星記","content":"還沒啃完2019所掉進的坑，結果我又掉進2020未來的坑 TT\n偶然在youtube看見GMMTV 2020 預播系列，\n發現了《千星記 A TALE OF THOUSAND STARS》\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/jefxhLC.jpg\n\n這部劇由球哥(Earth)和新人演員 Mix 主演\n故事講述主角Tian（Mix飾演）患上心臟病，\n因女主Toufan車禍身亡，而移植女主的心臟重生了。\n男主Tian從女主的遺物發現男主Phupha的照片，\n移植在他身上的心臟竟然不受控地狂跳了。\n為了完成女主的遺願，Tian決定到泰國邊界偏僻山地當志願老師。\n在那裡遇見了照片裡的Phupha,然後與Phupha日久生情的故事。\n\n預告：\n  \nhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=i8oIP9QBvgo\n \n\n結果看了預告之後，我就掉入深坑再也爬不起來了\n無論是顏值還是演員都很對我胃口 <3\n球哥的演技毋庸置疑，新人Mix的顏值也很不錯!\n只是GMMTV還沒確認真正的播出日期。\n不過現在微博已經有大神中翻小說版了，\n現在只出了第六章，每個星期五更一章。\n追到我好苦啊 TT\n\n然後OST很對我胃口!!!\n \nhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9Ic6PWwTU8g\n \n\n再附上有英文歌詞的版本\n \nhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=taVqYP7brTk\n \n\n感覺歌詞蠻符合劇情的~~\n\n歡迎大家與我討論看看有什麼2020大劇哦~","excerpt":"還沒啃完2019所掉進的坑，結果我又掉進2020未來的坑 TT，偶然在youtube看見GMMTV 2020 預播系列，發現了《千星記 A TALE OF THOUSAND STARS》這部劇由球哥（","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"e6b363d9-9ec0-450c-bdcc-7c0c30eb1084","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-12-23T14:46:32.063Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-30T13:00:27.202Z","commentCount":12,"likeCount":19,"tags":[],"topics":["泰劇","期待","BL"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":true,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"BL","forumAlias":"boyslove","school":"叫我姐姐","department":"kying_3","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":true,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":19}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/jefxhLC.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"8880ea31-9104-4646-a9b5-492691b5afcf","url":"https://i.imgur.com/jefxhLCl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/jefxhLCl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/jefxhLCl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["NO_NEED_ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-12-23T14:46:32.063Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-30T13:00:27.202Z"},{